    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with two pounds of gemstones. Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine gemstones, as well as smaller tumbled stones, the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones awaits! HOW TO USE: Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (scoop and sifting screen not included); dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed! Clean and dry found gemstones and rocks and store in included burlap drawstring bag for safekeeping</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 5lb Rough Gemstone Paydirt Bag Gold Panning Kits (8 Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with two pounds of gemstones. Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine gemstones, as well as smaller tumbled stones, the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones awaits!</p>\n  <p>HOW TO USE: Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (scoop and sifting screen not included); dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed! Clean and dry found gemstones and rocks and store in included burlap drawstring bag for safekeeping</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>GEMSTONE PAYDIRT:</strong> 5lb bag is packed with an assortment of genuine gemstones</li>\n    <li><strong>TOP QUALITY GEMSTONES:</strong> Discover gemstones like Amethyst, Labradorite and more</li>\n    <li><strong>HOW TO USE:</strong> Sift paydirt in bucket of water, remove gemstones and match to chart</li>\n    <li><strong>GOLD PANNING KIT:</strong> Perfect for hobbyists, rock collectors, and gold prospectors</li>\n    <li><strong>KIT INCLUDES:</strong> 5lb paydirt, burlap bag, instructions and gemstone ID chart</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73564/DNlR4t5eZ42SmujOjYcadEYI6NRw33-metaa2l0X2xnX2dlb2Rlc19oYW1tZXJfdXBkYXRlZC5qcGc=-.jpg\" alt=\"Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with two pounds of gemstones\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> PDB0005APARENT</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Use the gemstone identification chart to identify which gemstones you have.</p>\n  <p>Whether you&#039;re a seasoned gem enthusiast or a curious beginner, our gemstone paydirt delivers the thrill of sifting through rich, organic material to uncover genuine gemstones. Perfect for hobbyists, rock collectors and gold prospectors looking for a fun, hands on outdoor activity!</p>\n  <p>KIT INCLUDES: 5lb rough gemstone paydirt bag, 8 x 12 burlap cinch bag for rock and gemstone storage, paydirt screening instructions card and a double sided gemstone identification chart and information card</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Each five pound ASR Outdoor rough gemstone paydirt bag is a cornucopia of excitement and discovery, with two pounds of gemstones. Packed with a great variety of authentic and genuine gemstones, as well as smaller tumbled stones, the thrill of sifting through paydirt and identifying precious gemstones awaits! HOW TO USE: Fill a large bucket with water; scoop out paydirt into sifting screen (scoop and sifting screen not included); dip sifting screen into water to remove dirt and repeat with remaining paydirt; sift through material a second time to ensure no rocks or gemstones were missed! Clean and dry found gemstones and rocks and store in included burlap drawstring bag for safekeeping.",
